description:
Join us as we dive into the debut of 'The Hopeful,' a captivating film that chronicles the journey of Adventist pioneers. Discover how the Adventist Church is leading Digital Evangelism in the Philippines, empowering social media discipleship.Plus, hear about ADRA Tobago volunteers' inspiring efforts to clean up an oil spill after a barge wreck. 

Stay tuned as ANN brings everything you have to know about what is happening in the church around the world. For a deeper dive into these headlines, visit https://www.adventist.news

ANN is the official news channel of the Seventh-day Adventist Church.
